                        We are a digital home for painters, illustrators, photographers, and sculptors —
                        a place where creativity meets community, and every artwork finds an admirer somewhere
                        in the world.
                    </p>
                    <a href="#our-story" class="btn btn-gallery mt-3">
                        Discover More <i class="fa-solid fa-arrow-down ms-2"></i>
                    </a>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <a href="#our-story" class="hero-scroll-cue" aria-label="Scroll down">
            <i class="fa-solid fa-chevron-down"></i>
        </a>
