        <div class="container">
            <div class="row align-items-center g-5">
                <div class="col-lg-6 reveal">
                    <div class="story-image-wrap">
                        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1547891654-e66ed7ebb968?auto=format&fit=crop&w=900&q=80"
                             alt="Artist painting in a studio" class="img-fluid" />
                        <div class="story-badge">
                            <div class="num">2021</div>
                            <small class="text-muted-custom">Founded with a vision</small>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="col-lg-6 reveal">
                    <span class="section-eyebrow">Our Story</span>
                    <h2 class="section-title">Why We Built This Gallery</h2>
                    <p class="text-muted-custom">
                        Online Art Gallery began with a simple observation: too many gifted artists were
                        struggling to find an audience beyond their local circles, while art lovers everywhere
                        were searching for original, meaningful pieces they simply couldn't find nearby.
                    </p>
                    <p class="text-muted-custom">
                        We set out to close that gap — building a platform where artists can upload and
                        showcase paintings, digital art, illustrations, photography, and sculpture, and where
                        collectors can browse, search, and purchase with complete confidence. What started as
                        a small idea has grown into a thriving global community that supports artists and makes
                        art accessible to everyone, everywhere.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="mv-list mt-3">
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>Supporting independent artists worldwide</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>Making original art accessible to all</li>
                        <li><i class="fa-solid fa-circle-check"></i>Building trust between artists and collectors</li>
                    </ul>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
